manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Since 1960, Bronson has been providing families with the highest quality products available. This 60+ year heritage speaks for itself. But with so many online vitamin stores, why should you purchase supplements from Bronson? In short, our company is time proven, offering the purest, high quality vitamins backed by science. Bronson provides the very best natural health products for you and your family.

Bronson Vitamin B Complex with Vitamin C - Immune Health, Energy Support & Nervous System Support - Non-GMO Deficiency in B Vitamins can easily happen to anyone, which can cause the body to feel lethargic and rundown. Bronson’s Vitamin B Complex with Vitamin C includes an effective amount of B Vitamins combined with Vitamin C to support valuable daily replenishment within the body.* By containing all B Vitamins packed into one vegetarian capsule, Vitamin B Complex with C helps to support immune function, energy production and nervous system health.* Our Vitamin B Complex with Vitamin C is carefully manufactured and is Non-GMO, Gluten-Free and Soy-Free tested at our state of the art GMP Registered New York Facility.

B + C Daily Replenishment Deficiency in vitamins is a common occurrence. Bronson’s Vitamin B-Complex with Vitamin C can be taken daily to provide daily replenishment of key vitamins. Our B-Complex contains an effective amount of all B Vitamins combined with Vitamin C packed into a once daily vegetarian capsule. Immune, Energy & Nervous System Support Our Vitamin B-Complex includes key B vitamins combined with Vitamin C to support immune function.* Vitamin B Complex with C includes an effective amount of B vitamins to support energy production and proper nerve function.* GMP Manufacturer Bronson supplements are manufactured in our own GMP facility located in the United States, which includes regular on-site facility inspections to verify adherence to all US supplement manufacturing regulations. Such adherence to all required Good Manufacturing Practices (GMPs) and established Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) ensures the potency, identity, purity, and disintegration of all Bronson products. That’s why Bronson manufactures their own products – having complete control over the products we’re making and you’re taking is not something we're willing to trust to anyone else. Quality Pledge Bronson never compromises product quality and integrity. That’s why each supplement starts with the finest ingredients. Bronson laboratory expert’s evaluate all raw materials under strict, established procedures, rejecting any material that does not meet our stringent specifications. In addition, each Bronson supplement undergoes intense scrutiny during the manufacturing and packaging process to ensure our customers’ get the highest quality products possible.
* These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I work long hours indoors, often without seeing the sun. My doctor informed me of a vitamin D deficiency and recommended I take supplements. I've been using this product for a while now, and it appears to be quite effective. Taking one pill every morning provides me with a noticeable boost of energy. I love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value and quality
reviews.reviewText: This bottle of Vitamin B complex is well worth the price. The quality and quantity of this product is paramount to many other brands I've purchased online. I've worked in the vitamin retail industry year ago and could tell this is of highest quality available. I also like that it came in capsule form so that I could actually see inside the pill and tell if it's gone bad. The potency of the brand of vitamin b complex also impressed me as I could tell the benefits from it the first day I started taking it. I will have to reorder and purchase their multi-vitamins and minerals to try out.
